message: “Police arrest 2 suspects at North Carolina nail salon; suspects charged with human trafficking.”

data.description: DAVIDSON, N.C. -- The Davidson Police Department said two suspects are charged with human trafficking, involuntary servitude and conspiracy after they were picked up at a Davidson nail salon, WSOC reports.
